Program: Omnibus
Title: Teenagers
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376l47
Last Broadcast Date: 21 November 1995
Following teenagers on 'teen training' courses in Great Britain, learning techniques to improve relationships and do better at school. Followed by a discussion with Ben Renshaw, Marni Rolly, Dr Julia Brennan about teenagehood around the world.